2024-04-18 18:13:40.974 +05:30 [INF] Executed DbCommand (29ms) [Parameters=[@__productId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[ProductId], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductImage], [t].[ProductName], [t].[ProductStatusId], [t].[Quantity], [t].[StoreId], [t].[SubCategoryId], [p0].[ProductDetailId], [p0].[Attribute], [p0].[ProductId], [p0].[Value], [i].[ImageId], [i].[ImageName], [i].[ProductId], [i].[StoredImage]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[ProductId], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductImage], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ProductStatusId], [p].[Quantity], [p].[StoreId], [p].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = @__productId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductDetails] AS [p0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
